  <ThingDef ParentName="RH_TET_Skaven_ArmorHelmetMakeableBase">
    <defName>RH_TET_Skaven_Apparel_GasMask</defName>
    <label>skaven gas-mask</label>
    <description>A  makeshift skaven gas mask, frequently employed by the poisoned-wind globadiers and mortar teams of Clan Skryre. It may offer decent protection against damage and poison, but it's by no means a perfect mask. Holes in the cloth, breathing tubes, or air filters often mean that some globadiers will still die at the hands of their own fearsome weaponry.</description>
